snippet.title: VENOM: THE LAST DANCE - New Hindi Trailer | In Cinemas October 25
snippet.description:
With you to the end.

Witness the epic conclusion in #Venom: The Last Dance - exclusively in cinemas on October 25. Releasing in English, Hindi, Tamil & Telugu.

In Venom: The Last Dance, Tom Hardy returns as Venom, one of Marvel’s greatest and most complex characters, for the final film in the trilogy. Eddie and Venom are on the run. Hunted by both of their worlds and with the net closing in, the duo are forced into a devastating decision that will bring the curtains down on Venom and Eddie's last dance.
 
Venom: The Last Dance stars Tom Hardy, Chiwetel Ejiofor, Juno Temple, Rhys Ifans, Peggy Lu, Alanna Ubach and Stephen Graham. The film is directed by Kelly Marcel from a screenplay she wrote, based on a story by Hardy and Marcel. The film is produced by Avi Arad, Matt Tolmach, Amy Pascal, Kelly Marcel, Tom Hardy and Hutch Parker.
 
Directed by:​​ Kelly Marcel​​

snippet.title: 1st T20I | Highlights | Australia Tour Of England | 11th September 2024
snippet.description:
In the 1st T20I, England won the toss and elected to bowl first. Australia posted 179 runs and became all out by 19.3 overs. Travis Head was the top scorer with a terrific knock of 59 from 23 balls. Later, Australian bowlers troubled England batters and kept on taking wickets. England lost all 10 wickets for 151 runs as Australia sealed a 28-run win in the end.
.

snippet.description: In this video join me as we celebrate Alandra's birthday. I made a custom dress and also made a cat cake. snippet.title: Kaffara Episode 47 - [Eng Sub] - Ali Ansari - Laiba Khan - Zoya Nasir - 12th September 2024
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Kaffara Episode 47 - [Eng Sub] - Ali Ansari - Laiba Khan - Zoya Nasir - 12th September 2024 - HAR PAL GEO

Sitara, a lively orphan living with her brother, aunt, and uncle, finds joy in life's small things despite her aunt's poor treatment. Her aunt keeps her around because she has a share in the family's property.
Salar, the son of a wealthy businessman, is passionate about photography, which often earns him criticism from his family. With a pure heart, Salar is known for evading his responsibilities.
At her cousin's wedding, Sitara wrongly assumes Salar is the photographer. Salar develops a soft spot for Sitara after seeing how poorly she is treated. However, due to a conspiracy, objections arise about their closeness. Salar, once again, avoids the issue, leaving Sitara to face doubts from her own family.
Can Sitara prove she’s not guilty? Will Salar help her avoid further mistreatment? Will her family support Sitara? Can Salar show he genuinely cares? Will there be more plots against Sitara?

snippet.title: Introducing iPhone 16 Pro | Apple
snippet.description:
This is iPhone 16 Pro. Built for Apple Intelligence. A new powerful, private, personal, deeply integrated intelligence system to help you get things done effortlessly.

Powered by the new supercharged A18 Pro chip, with a faster Neural Engine, and an improved CPU and GPU. Which levels up both your iPhone and your gaming experience, offering our best-ever graphics performance.

Plus there’s an all-new camera system and an all-new way to control it. Use Camera Control to instantly access your camera, adjust settings, and take a photo.

And you can now shoot video in 4K 120 fps Dolby Vision to capture and edit stunningly cinematic slow motion.

Built with titanium. And featuring our thinnest borders for an even larger display.

iPhone 16 Pro is the most innovative, most powerful, and most intelligent iPhone ever. From the inside out.

Learn more about iPhone 16 Pro and iPhone 16 Pro Max: https://apple.co/4dSqFbR

Audio Descriptions: https://apple.co/4dTrRvG

snippet.title: Rooh (Official Video) Amrita Virk | R Nait | Naiqra Kaur | Mad Mix | Punjabi Song 2024
snippet.description:
R Nait Music & Rajchet Sharma Presents "Rooh" by R Nait and Amrita Virk is a lively and heartwarming Punjabi track that blends traditional beats with a rich regional flavor. The song is set in a playful, conversational tone, making it feel like an engaging exchange between two people. It beautifully weaves themes of love, attachment, and the joy of being together, all while maintaining a lighthearted and fun atmosphere. The song’s breezy vibe and authentic musical elements capture the essence of a joyful connection.

snippet.description:

Episode 4188: Decoration Ka Theme Kya Hai?
--------------------------------------------------------
The men in the colony are eager to know the theme the women have chosen for the Ganpati celebrations, but their wives are tight-lipped about it.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - Ep 4188 | 12 Sep 2024
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2024 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #16yearsoftmkoc  #4000episodes

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/shows/taarak-mehta-ka-ooltah-chashmah-1090380639

snippet.title: Kaffara Episode 46 - [Eng Sub] - Ali Ansari - Laiba Khan - Zoya Nasir - 11th September 2024
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Kaffara Episode 46 - [Eng Sub] - Ali Ansari - Laiba Khan - Zoya Nasir - 11th September 2024 - HAR PAL GEO

Sitara, a lively orphan living with her brother, aunt, and uncle, finds joy in life's small things despite her aunt's poor treatment. Her aunt keeps her around because she has a share in the family's property.
Salar, the son of a wealthy businessman, is passionate about photography, which often earns him criticism from his family. With a pure heart, Salar is known for evading his responsibilities.
At her cousin's wedding, Sitara wrongly assumes Salar is the photographer. Salar develops a soft spot for Sitara after seeing how poorly she is treated. However, due to a conspiracy, objections arise about their closeness. Salar, once again, avoids the issue, leaving Sitara to face doubts from her own family.
Can Sitara prove she’s not guilty? Will Salar help her avoid further mistreatment? Will her family support Sitara? Can Salar show he genuinely cares? Will there be more plots against Sitara?

snippet.title: Aaj Bhi 2 (Video) Vishal Mishra | Kaushal Kishore | VYRL Originals
snippet.description:
A follow up to Aaj Bhi which ended up capturing millions of hearts upon its release back in 2020, Aaj Bhi 2 is just the perfect sequel to Aaj Bhi. Sung and composed by the sensational Vishal Mishra, Aaj Bhi 2 explores the raw, painful reality of loss. Vishal’s voice perfectly captures the loneliness, regret, and the overwhelming sadness of separation. Kaushal Kishore’s lyrics conveys the haunting reality of heartbreak and how healing is never a linear process, and one keeps getting sucked into their past searching for the moments where everything seemed right. Vishal’s composition and vocals brings Kaushal Kishore’s heartbreaking words alive and carries each lyric like a heavy weight, in what is an extremely powerful and emotional medley. Aaj Bhi 2 feels like a warm hug after a long rainy day.

🎶 Listen Aaj Bhi 2 🎧 Now On 📲

snippet.title: We Are Not Afraid To Die Class 11 | Chapter 2 English | Questions And Answers/Summary/One Shot
snippet.description:
We Are Not Afraid To Die Class 11 | Chapter 2 English | Questions And Answers/Summary/One Shot/Explanation

In this video, we bring you a complete and engaging explanation of We Are Not Afraid to Die... If We Can All Be Together, which is Chapter 2 of the Class 11 English NCERT textbook. This chapter is based on a real-life adventure, narrating the intense and thrilling experience of a family that embarks on a journey to sail around the world. Their courage, determination, and unity in the face of life-threatening storms form the core of this story, making it an essential part of Class 11 English.

We covered a detailed summary of Chapter 2 to help students grasp the storyline and themes clearly. This video also covers important questions and answers for Class 11 English that are often asked in exams, giving you the edge to score well. Whether you’re revising for exams or trying to understand the chapter in-depth, this video will guide you through key takeaways and provide an easy-to-understand explanation of We Are Not Afraid to Die Class 11.

In addition to the summary and questions, we’ll discuss the chapter’s themes, character analysis, and important lessons, ensuring you get a holistic understanding of Class 11 English Chapter 2. With this one-shot video, you can quickly revise the chapter, prepare for exams, and build a strong foundation in literature.

Watch this Class 11 English Chapter 2 summary and question-answer video to make your exam preparation smoother. Don't forget to subscribe for more videos on Class 11 English important chapters, summaries, and question answers!

snippet.title: How to get the Mega Knight Evo FOR FREE!!
snippet.description:
Get the Mega Knight for FREE! Starting September 14 at 9 AM UTC, collect crowns to unlock Mega Knight Evolution Shards, Gold, Chests, and more!

Don't miss the Creator Showdown on Twitch.tv/clashroyale!


Twitter ► https://twitter.com/ClashRoyale/
Instagram ► https://www.instagram.com/clashroyale
TikTok ► https://www.tiktok.com/@clashroyale
Facebook ► https://www.facebook.com/ClashRoyale/

ENTER THE ARENA
Build your Battle Deck and outsmart the enemy in fast real-time battles. From the creators of CLASH OF CLANS comes a real-time multiplayer battle game starring your favourite Clash characters and more. Start battling against players from around the world!

BECOME A MASTER OF STRATEGY AND DECK BUILDING
Choose unique Cards to your Battle Deck and head to the Arena for Battle!
Place your Cards right and knock down the enemy King and Princesses from their Towers in a strategic and fast-paced match.

COLLECT AND UPGRADE 100+ CARDS
Hog Rider! Collect and upgrade 100+ Cards featuring the Clash of Clans troops, spells and defences you know and love and many others. Win battles and progress to new Arenas to unlock powerful new Cards to your collection!

BATTLE YOUR WAY TO THE TOP
Battle your way to the League and Global Tournaments to match against the best players in the world.
Compete for glory and rewards!

SEASONAL EVENTS
Unlock new Seasonal items like Tower Skins, Emotes and powerful Magic Items with the Season Pass and participate in fun Challenges that put your skills to the test!

JOIN A CLAN AND GO TO WAR
Join or form a Clan with other players to share Cards and battle in Clan Wars for BIG rewards!

See you in the Arena!
#ClashRoyale

Episode 4187: Mahila Mandal's Decoration Planning
--------------------------------------------------------
The women of Gokuldham are thrilled to welcome Bappa and have taken charge of all the decorations. However, they want to keep their decoration idea a secret from everyone. 

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni

Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2024 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #16yearsoftmkoc  #4000episodes

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Kaffara Episode 45 - [Eng Sub] - Ali Ansari - Laiba Khan - Zoya Nasir - 10th September 2024 - HAR PAL GEO

Sitara, a lively orphan living with her brother, aunt, and uncle, finds joy in life's small things despite her aunt's poor treatment. Her aunt keeps her around because she has a share in the family's property.
Salar, the son of a wealthy businessman, is passionate about photography, which often earns him criticism from his family. With a pure heart, Salar is known for evading his responsibilities.
At her cousin's wedding, Sitara wrongly assumes Salar is the photographer. Salar develops a soft spot for Sitara after seeing how poorly she is treated. However, due to a conspiracy, objections arise about their closeness. Salar, once again, avoids the issue, leaving Sitara to face doubts from her own family.
Can Sitara prove she’s not guilty? Will Salar help her avoid further mistreatment? Will her family support Sitara? Can Salar show he genuinely cares? Will there be more plots against Sitara?

snippet.description:
"The GOAT" (The Goofiest Of All Time) is a Tamil film that falls under the 'milking' genre. Staying true to the genre, Venkat Prabhu has given a compilation of 'brainrot reels' that tries to harvest nostalgia, disguised as a movie. Thalapathy, Ilaya Thalapathy, Ilalaya Thalapathy and Ilalalaya Thalapathy have played pivotal roles in this goofy ahh film.

snippet.title: PlayStation 5 Pro Console - Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
PlayStation®5 Pro Console

Witness Play Unleashed™

With the PlayStation®5 Pro console, the world’s greatest game creators can enhance their games with incredible features like advanced ray tracing, super sharp image clarity for your 4K TV, and high frame rate gameplay.* That means you get to play PS5® games with the most impressive visuals ever possible on a PlayStation® console, and with 2TB of SSD storage included, your favorite games will be ready and waiting for you to jump right in for your next awesome adventure.**

PlayStation® Spectral Super Resolution (PSSR) 
Get super sharp image clarity on your 4K TV using AI enhanced resolution for ultra-high definition play with astonishing detail.*

Optimized Console Performance 
Reach higher and more consistent frame rates for silky smooth gameplay with support for 60Hz and 120Hz displays.*

Advanced Ray Tracing 
Experience next level realism with ray traced reflections, shadows, and high-quality global illumination as you explore stunning game worlds.*

*Feature only available on select PS5® games that have been enhanced for PS5® Pro when compared with PS5®. PS5® Pro enhanced features will vary by game. 

**A portion of the SSD is reserved for system software and other functions so the available SSD capacity may vary.

#ps5 #ps5pro #playstation

snippet.title: Deva Shree Ganesha - 8K/4K Video | Ganpati Song | Agneepath | Priyanka Chopra | Hrithik Roshan
snippet.description:
Experience the divine energy and vibrant spirit of Ganesh Chaturthi with the mesmerizing 8K/4K video of "Deva Shree Ganesha" from the blockbuster movie Agneepath. 
 
#devashreeganesha #hrithikroshan #priyankachopra #agneepath #ajayatul #ajaygogavale #ganeshsongs #ganpatisongs #ganpatibappamorya 

Credits :
Song Title- Deva Shree Ganesha 
Movie- Agneepath (2012) 
Singer- Ajay Gogavale 
Lyrics- Amitabh Bhattacharya 
Music- Ajay-Atul
Video remastered by @MusicRemaster 

Song Lyrics :
Jwaala Si Jalti Hai Aankhon Mein Jiske Bhi
Dil Mein Tera Naam Hai
Parwah Hi Kya Uska Aarambh Kaisa Hai
Aur Kaisa Parinam Hai
Dharti Ambar Sitaare
Uski Nazarein Utaarein
Dar Bhi Us Se Daraa Re
Jiski Rakhwaliyan Re Karta Saya Tera
Deva Shree Ganesha (X8)

Ho Teri Bhakti Ka Vardan Hai
Jo Kamaye Wo Dhanwan Hai
Bin Kinaare Ki Kashti Hai Woh
Deva Tujhse Jo Anjaan Hai
Yoon To Mooshak Sawari Teri
Sab Pe Hai Peharedaari Teri
Paap Ki Aandhiyan Laakh Hon
Kabhi Jyoti Na Haari Teri
Apni Takdeer Ka Woh Khud Sikandar Hua Re
Bhool Ke Yeh Jahan Re Jis Kisi Ne Yahan Re
Saath Paaya Tera Hey
Deva Shree Ganesha X (8)

Ho Teri Dhooli Ka Teeka Kiye
Deva Jo Bhakt Tera Jiye
Use Amrit Ka Hai Moh Kya
Hans Ke Vish Ka Woh Pyaala Piye
Teri Mahima Ke Chhaya Tale
Kaal Ke Rath Ka Pahiya Chale
Ek Chingari Pratishodh Se
Khadi Raavan Ki Lanka Jale
Shatruon Ki Kataarein Ik Akele Se Haarein
Kan Bhi Parbat Hua Re, Shlok Ban Ke Jahan Re
Naam Aaya Tera Hey
Deva Shree Ganesha X (8)

Ganpati Bappa Moreya
Ghalin Lotangan Vandin Charan
Dolyani Pahin Rup Tujhe
Deva Preme Alingan Anande Pujin
Bhave Ovaleen Mhane Nama

Twameva Mata,Cha Phita Twameva
Twameva Bandhuscha Sakha Twamevaa....
Twameva Vidya,Dravinum Twameva
Twameva Sarvam Mama Deva Devaaa

Kayena Vacha Manasendriyenva
Buddhyatmana Va Prakritiswabhavat
Karoomi Yadhyath Sakalam Parasmai
Narayanayeti Samarpayami

Achyutam Keshavam Ramnarayanam
Krushanadamodaram Vasudevam Bhaje
Shridharam Madhavam Gopikavallabham
Janaki Nayakam Ramchandra Bhaje

Hare Raam Hare Raam
Raam Raam Hare Hareee
Hare Krishna Hare Krishna
Krishna Krishna Hare Hareee
Hare Raam Hare Raam
Raam Raam Hare Hareeee
Hare Krishna Hare Krishna
Krishna Krishna Hare Hareee

snippet.title: Millennials vs Gen Z | Funcho
snippet.description:
First of all HAPPY GANESH CHATURTHI🙏🙏
Well this generation has changed so much. Me and Shyam being a millennials but having GENZ friends gave us this insight about them. 
Hum bhi kahin na kahin GenZ ke saath rehke same harkatein karne lag gaye hai 😅
But this video is pure exaggeration, GenZ itne bhi danger nahi hote hai.  Please take it in a funny way only.
Hum toh khud GenZ jaise rehte hai. 
Hope you enjoyed our take on this new generation.
LIKE SHARE COMMENT. See you soon ♥️

snippet.title: VENOM: THE LAST DANCE - Trailer Countdown
snippet.description:
Since you asked nicely. 

The final #Venom: The Last Dance trailer drops this Thursday.

Visit our site: https://venom.movie/

Follow Us On Social:

Subscribe to the Sony Pictures YouTube Channel for more exclusive content: http://bit.ly/SonyPicsSubscribe 

In Venom: The Last Dance, Tom Hardy returns as Venom, one of Marvel’s greatest and most complex characters, for the final film in the trilogy. Eddie and Venom are on the run. Hunted by both of their worlds and with the net closing in, the duo are forced into a devastating decision that will bring the curtains down on Venom and Eddie's last dance.
 
Venom: The Last Dance stars Tom Hardy, Chiwetel Ejiofor, Juno Temple, Rhys Ifans, Peggy Lu, Alanna Ubach and Stephen Graham. The film is directed by Kelly Marcel from a screenplay she wrote, based on a story by Hardy and Marcel. The film is produced by Avi Arad, Matt Tolmach, Amy Pascal, Kelly Marcel, Tom Hardy and Hutch Parker.

In Venom: The Last Dance, Tom Hardy returns as Venom, one of Marvel’s greatest and most complex characters, for the final film in the trilogy. Eddie and Venom are on the run. Hunted by both of their worlds and with the net closing in, the duo are forced into a devastating decision that will bring the curtains down on Venom and Eddie's last dance.
 
Venom: The Last Dance stars Tom Hardy, Chiwetel Ejiofor, Juno Temple, Rhys Ifans, Peggy Lu, Alanna Ubach and Stephen Graham. The film is directed by Kelly Marcel from a screenplay she wrote, based on a story by Hardy and Marcel. The film is produced by Avi Arad, Matt Tolmach, Amy Pascal, Kelly Marcel, Tom Hardy and Hutch Parker.

Episode 4186: Ganpati Decorations
--------------------------------------------------------
The women of Gokuldham want to take charge of the Ganpati decorations and propose their idea to the colony members Will the members agree to let them handle the decorations

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - Ep 4186 | 10 Sep 2024
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2024 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #16yearsoftmkoc  #4000episodes

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
